                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">2. What Are Incoterms and Why Do They Matter?</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Incoterms (International Commercial Terms) define who is responsible for what during the shipping process. Understanding these terms is essential for accurate cost calculation and risk management.</p>
                    
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
