                                    <td class="p-3">Experienced importers with own logistics</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="bg-green-50">
                                    <td class="p-3 font-bold text-green-600">FOB</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Free on Board</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Port of loading</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Most common for sea freight</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="bg-blue-50">
                                    <td class="p-3 font-bold text-blue-600">CIF</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Cost Insurance Freight</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Port of loading</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Buyer wants insurance included</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="bg-blue-50">
                                    <td class="p-3 font-bold text-blue-600">DDP</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Delivered Duty Paid</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Buyer's premises</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Turnkey solution, higher price</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr class="bg-amber-50">
                                    <td class="p-3 font-bold text-amber-600">DAP</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Delivered at Place</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Named place</td>
                                    <td class="p-3">Buyer pays duties separately</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
                        <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4">Recommended Incoterms for Chargers</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3"><strong>FOB Shenzhen / FOB Guangzhou:</strong> Most common and recommended for most importers. The seller handles factory preparation and port handling; you arrange main carriage and insurance.</p>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-3"><strong>DDP (Delivered Duty Paid):</strong> Best for new importers who want a single invoice covering everything. The seller handles all logistics including duties.</p>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>EXW:</strong> Only recommended if you have established relationships with freight forwarders and can arrange all logistics efficiently.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                </section>

