                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">3. Shipping Options: Sea, Air & Express</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Choosing the right shipping method depends on your order volume, urgency, and budget. Here's a detailed comparison:</p>

                    <div class="space-y-6">
