                <!-- Section 4 -->
                <section id="landed-cost" class="mb-16">
                <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic mb-6">4. OEM Landed Cost: FOB vs DDP & Total Cost Calculation</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Total Landed Cost (TLC) is the complete cost of getting your products to your warehouse, including all fees and duties. Here's how to calculate it:</p>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
                        <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4">Landed Cost Formula</h3>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm mb-4">
                            <p class="mb-2">TLC = Product Cost + Freight + Insurance + MFN Duty + Section 301 + Port Fees + Last Mile</p>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
                            <li><strong>Product Cost:</strong> FOB price from supplier.</li>
                            <li><strong>Freight:</strong> sea ($0.05-0.15 per unit) or air ($0.30-0.80 per unit).</li>
                            <li><strong>Insurance:</strong> typically 0.2-0.5% of cargo value (CIF).</li>
                            <li><strong>MFN Duty:</strong> HTS code base rate × CIF value (HTS 8504.40.95 wireless chargers: 0% MFN; 8504.40.85 USB and car chargers: 2.5% MFN).</li>
                            <li><strong>Section 301:</strong> up to 25% surcharge for China origin under HTS 8504 unless an active exclusion applies. Current exclusions are extended to November 10, 2026.</li>
                            <li><strong>Port Fees:</strong> terminal handling and congestion surcharges.</li>
                            <li><strong>Last Mile:</strong> trucking to your warehouse or to an Amazon FBA destination.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-brandBlue/5 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
                        <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-4">Example Calculation: 5,000 Wireless Chargers (HTS 8504.40.95)</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Product Cost (FOB Shenzhen)</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$15,000</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Sea Freight (40HC China to US West)</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$3,000 ($0.60/unit)</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Insurance (0.3%)</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$54</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">CIF Value</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$18,054</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">MFN Duty (HTS 8504.40.95: 0%)</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$0</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Section 301 (25% on China origin)</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$4,514</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Port Handling & Fees</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$350</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-600">Last Mile Delivery</span>
                                <span class="font-bold">$400</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between font-black text-brandBlue pt-2">
                                <span>TOTAL LANDED COST</span>
                                <span>$23,318</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between text-brandOrange font-bold">
                                <span>Cost Per Unit</span>
                                <span>$4.66 (vs. $3.00 FOB)</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm"><strong>Key Insight:</strong> Section 301 alone now adds 25% to CIF for most China-origin chargers, lifting landed cost roughly 55% above FOB on a 5,000-unit wireless charger order. With the $800 de minimis closed, the same math applies to small parcel and FBA direct shipments. Verify exclusions and apply them with a licensed customs broker before booking.</p>
                </div>
